OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774246422
OL,3,CPolice investigate antisemitic hate
OL,4,Ccrime after ambulances set alight in
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FPolice are investigating an
OL,8,Fantisemitic hate crime after an
OL,9,Fapparent arson attack on four
OL,10,Fambulances belonging to the Jewish
OL,11,FCommunity Ambulance service in London,
OL,12,Fthe Metropolitan Police said.
OL,14,FOfficers were called to Highfield
OL,15,FRoad, Golders Green around 1.45am on
OL,16,FMonday after receiving reports of a
OL,17,Ffire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774246422
OL,3,CPolice investigate antisemitic hate
OL,4,Ccrime after ambulances set alight in
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FThe Met confirmed the incident is
OL,8,Fbeing treated as an antisemitic hate
OL,9,Fcrime, while the London Fire Brigade
OL,10,Fsaid no injuries had been reported.
OL,12,FSuperintendent Sarah Jackson, who
OL,13,Fleads policing in the local area,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We know this incident will
OL,15,Fcause a great deal of community
OL,16,Fconcern and officers remain on scene
OL,17,Fto carry out urgent enquiries.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774246422
OL,3,CPolice investigate antisemitic hate
OL,4,Ccrime after ambulances set alight in
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,F"We are in the process of examining
OL,8,FCCTV and are aware of online footage.
OL,9,FWe believe we are looking for three
OL,10,Fsuspects at this early stage.
OL,12,F"There have been no arrests yet, and
OL,13,Fwe would urge anyone with information
OL,14,Fto please contact us as soon as
OL,15,Fpossible ` you can do so anonymously
OL,16,Fif you wish.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774246422
OL,3,CPolice investigate antisemitic hate
OL,4,Ccrime after ambulances set alight in
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,F"We will be engaging with faith
OL,8,Fleaders and carrying out additional
OL,9,Fpatrols in the local area as we
OL,10,Fcontinue our investigation to provide
OL,11,Freassurance and a highly visible
OL,12,Fpresence."
OL,14,FPolice said reports of explosions are
OL,15,Fbelieved to be linked to gas canisters
OL,16,Fon board the ambulances.
OL,18,FNearby homes were evacuated as a
OL,19,Fprecaution and road closures in the
OL,20,Farea remain in place.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
