OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774246422
OL,3,CPolice investigate antisemitic hate
OL,4,Ccrime after ambulances set alight in
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FShomrim, a non-profit organisation
OL,8,Fwhich operates a neighbourhood watch
OL,9,Fin the Golders Green neighbourhood,
OL,10,Fsaid it was "aware of loud explosions"
OL,11,Fearly on Monday morning.
OL,13,F"Emergency services are on scene
OL,14,Ffollowing a deliberate incident
OL,15,Finvolving _Hatzola ambulances being
OL,16,Fset alight," the group said in a post
OL,17,Fon X.
OL,26,@rD@MOUrD@fO]uD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774246422
OL,3,CPolice investigate antisemitic hate
OL,4,Ccrime after ambulances set alight in
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,F"The explosions were caused by oxygen
OL,8,Ftanks not a bomb or explosive device.
OL,9,FAlthough some buildings have been
OL,10,Fevacuated no casualties have been
OL,11,Freported.
OL,13,F"Please avoid the area while
OL,14,Finvestigations continue."
OL,16,FShomrim said Northwest London facility
OL,17,Frun by fellow Jewish charity Hatzola
OL,18,Fremained fully operational.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUvD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
