OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774246422
OL,3,CPolice investigate antisemitic hate
OL,4,Ccrime after ambulances set alight in
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FHatzola, which was established in 1979
OL,8,Fand is run by volunteers, provides
OL,9,Ffree medical transportation and
OL,10,Femergency response to those living in
OL,11,FNorth London.
OL,13,FThe fire brigade said around 40
OL,14,Ffirefighters were called to the fires
OL,15,Fand that multiple cylinders on the
OL,16,Fvehicles had exploded, causing windows
OL,17,Fto break in nearby flats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
