PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774246422
OL,3,CPolice investigate antisemitic hate
OL,4,Ccrime after ambulances set alight in
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FGolders Green ward councillor Dean
OL,8,FCohen, who was at the scene, told
OL,9,FJewish News the fact the incident was
OL,10,Ftaking place in the "car park of a
OL,11,Fsynagogue is particularly chilling and
OL,12,Fwill send shockwaves through our
OL,13,Fcommunity at a time of already
OL,14,Fheightened fears over antisemitism in
OL,15,Fthe UK".
OL,17,FHe said: "It's beyond time for the
OL,18,Fauthorities to wake and do more to
OL,19,Ftackle this hate running riot."
OL,26,@rD@UOUwD@GO]yD@JOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
