OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774246422
OL,3,CPolice investigate antisemitic hate
OL,4,Ccrime after ambulances set alight in
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FCommunity Security Trust (CST), a
OL,8,Fcharity which monitors antisemitism in
OL,9,Fthe UK, confirmed in a statement on X
OL,10,Fthat it was assisting police in their
OL,11,Fenquiries.
OL,13,FThe statement said: "We are aware of
OL,14,Fmultiple Hatzola ambulances that have
OL,15,Fbeen deliberately set alight in London.
OL,17,F"This has obvious comparison to
OL,18,Fsimilar antisemitic arson attacks
OL,19,Frecently in Belgium and the
OL,20,FNetherlands.
OL,26,@uD@UOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
